_:Nd4e479e564534ac788f2187c2133f7be <http://schema.org/description> "We’re the Driver and Vehicle Licensing Agency (DVLA), maintaining nearly 53 million driver records and more than 47 million vehicle records. Last year (2024 to 2025), we collected £8.4 billion in Vehicle Excise Duty (VED). DVLA is an executive agency, sponsored by the Department for Transport ." .
